text: Ei Ei Thet (born 13 December 1992) is a Burmese swimmer. She competed in the women's 50 metre freestyle event at the 2016 Summer Olympics, where she ranked 70th with a time of 30.25 seconds. She did not advance to the semifinals. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Burmese female swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Myanmar Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
